OL,3,GWales
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FEarly mist and low cloud will
OL,6,Fquickly burn away to leave a sunny
OL,7,Fday. Dry for many, but there is a
OL,8,Fsmall chance of the odd thunderstorm
OL,9,Fdeveloping later in the day. Feeling
OL,10,Fhot with high levels of UV expected.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FRemaining dry this evening
OL,13,Fwith plenty of late evening sunshine.
OL,14,FOvernight may see a few mist patches
OL,15,Freform but most remaining clear.
OL,16,FStaying warm with temperatures only
OL,17,Fslowly falling away.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
